{"tid":941293,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Linus Trovalds: Linux Desktop 唔掂係因為各自為政","createTime":"2018-12-14T16:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T06:17:28.000Z","uid":12599,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb19aa1b8fcf1045867f08f3117122e343fdd65b","tid":941293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e8oeN9AF4G8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe8oeN9AF4G8&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5d8fc156\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e8oeN9AF4G8</a><br />\n<br />\n劈頭第一句: chromeos 係最好嘅linux desktop distro, 跟住係android,特別係11月chromeos 開始原生支援debian<br />\n<br />\n佢希望chromeos 可以做好示範作用做為業界標準，令市場有更好用嘅linux desktop<br />\n<br />\nlinux仲未有大眾認可嘅desktop os, 唔係kernel問題，係desktop 開發者同distro 太散亂,chromeos 嘅示範作用係crouton中展示左linux kernel 係不同distro間係可以共用，需要用到特殊distro 功能只要安裝相應軟件就ok,無需要下下kernel 級重裝(containerized Linux distro)<br />\n<br />\n係呢個模式下硬件可以近乎100%使用，因為唔係經VM 做virtualization而係可以直接使用到kernel, 唯一問題係考量到安全性，修改kernel反而會麻煩左<br />\n<br />\n其實android 係有ms office 同adobe部份軟件，只係未到full version<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n軟件開發上linux已有swift,理論上已經可以開發native ios 同mac app, 加上係原生linux 架構，development上甚至比macos 更有優勢"},{"pid":"890caaad7d92c56e9123b1f1dfa4263cbefc4655","tid":941293,"uid":95172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"次次見到佢個樣，都諗起企鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企鵝大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f8011a5042e6174a83e4c8c0be595f9b6b8c9a","tid":941293,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"c10c1cb078e6146e164804e22c6bfc669589108a","tid":941293,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"生物演化本身就係各自為政，各個 linux desktop distro 各自演化其實自然生態現象"},{"pid":"e45413bf7e813f39e3d148bf7491ec43d6aa4e56","tid":941293,"uid":105553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb19aa1b8fcf1045867f08f3117122e343fdd65b","tid":941293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e8oeN9AF4G8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe8oeN9AF4G8&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5d8fc156\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e8oeN9AF4G8</a><br />\n<br />\n劈頭第一句: chromeos 係最好嘅linux desktop distro, 跟住係android,特別係11月chromeos 開始原生支援debian<br />\n<br />\n佢希望chromeos 可以做好示範作用做為業界標準，令市場有更好用嘅linux desktop<br />\n<br />\nlinux仲未有大眾認可嘅desktop os, 唔係kernel問題，係desktop 開發者同distro 太散亂,chromeos 嘅示範作用係crouton中展示左linux kernel 係不同distro間係可以共用，需要用到特殊distro 功能只要安裝相應軟件就ok,無需要下下kernel 級重裝(containerized Linux distro)<br />\n<br />\n係呢個模式下硬件可以近乎100%使用，因為唔係經VM 做virtualization而係可以直接使用到kernel, 唯一問題係考量到安全性，修改kernel反而會麻煩左<br />\n<br />\n其實android 係有ms office 同adobe部份軟件，只係未到full version<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n軟件開發上linux已有swift,理論上已經可以開發native ios 同mac app, 加上係原生linux 架構，development上甚至比macos 更有優勢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"distro版本零碎問題我響高登同呢度都講過唔止一次。而家連Linus Torvalds都咁講，佢又係hater。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6559249&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6559249%26page%3D1&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=79697fc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6559249&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/840341/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/840341/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c8804da06768ef1bce0aefc53e4aa2c211453d90","tid":941293,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"乜 distro 零碎唔係linux專登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8295a8b8fe03df5131742d43ee4e3c82542de529","tid":941293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8804da06768ef1bce0aefc53e4aa2c211453d90","tid":941293,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"乜 distro 零碎唔係linux專登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T00:51:42.000Z","msg":"唔係linux kernel 本身嘅用意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLinux kernel 始終得一個，由linus部濕鳩電腦做merging, 發佈patch linus 都有最終決定權，詳細可以睇返佢個TED talk<br />\n<br />\nLinux 講緊只係kernel部份，上面用GNU 定apache 定BSD 定close source Linus自己wfc, 只係你搞kernel一定要open source同用GNU license<br />\n<br />\nchromeos 本身用chromium os 個apache license, 涉及到商業野嘅source code 可以close source, linus 自己都覺得咁先係linux desktop嘅未來"},{"pid":"d84603199a16812e5dee391a0b9cdf90b0854e5d","tid":941293,"uid":51123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"唔掂係因為純用 UI 嘅人唔會理你底層有幾威<br />\n<br />\n有 Word Excel PowerPoint 已經夠，一個 Window License 用十年<br />\n<br />\n就不時禁下 Save 制，兩三日一次嘅藍畫面根本唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用 Linux Desktop 仲要學個新 UI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係佢地角度零得著"},{"pid":"65ec4a434b228d3124091fdb42fbdee05be78d88","tid":941293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d84603199a16812e5dee391a0b9cdf90b0854e5d","tid":941293,"uid":51123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"唔掂係因為純用 UI 嘅人唔會理你底層有幾威<br />\n<br />\n有 Word Excel PowerPoint 已經夠，一個 Window License 用十年<br />\n<br />\n就不時禁下 Save 制，兩三日一次嘅藍畫面根本唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用 Linux Desktop 仲要學個新 UI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係佢地角度零得著"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"Google office 而家好用過ms office好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nchromeos 最基本版得個chrome, 點樣難用過windows同mac嘅UI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96228b799431a7d830618e0dc0d7f462b00fb898","tid":941293,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8295a8b8fe03df5131742d43ee4e3c82542de529","tid":941293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8804da06768ef1bce0aefc53e4aa2c211453d90","tid":941293,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"乜 distro 零碎唔係linux專登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T00:51:42.000Z","msg":"唔係linux kernel 本身嘅用意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg